addHabitat(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint2.details: Add a habitat to the world map.

params.nectar: The amount of nectar in the habitat. Range from 1 to 100
params.pollen: The amount of pollen in the habitat. Range from 1 to 100
params.sap: The amount of sap in the habitat. Range from 1 to 100

forage(uint256,uint256).details: Forage resources from a habitat. The amount of resources gathered is based on the bee's foraging skill. After each forage, the resources in the habitat decrease by 5% and bee energy is decreased.

returns.nectarGathered: The amount of nectar gathered. pollenGathered The amount of pollen gathered. sapGathered The amount of sap gathered. The constant value ensure that the resources gathered are minimum at 20 quantity.

getAmountEnergyDeductionAfterForage(uint.details: Get the initial resources in a habitat.

returns._0: The amount of nectar, pollen, and sap in the habitat.

getAmountProductivityBoostAfterForage(ui.details: Get the amount of productivity boost after foraging in a habitat.

returns._0: The amount of productivity boost after foraging.

getHabitatResources(uint256).details: Get the resources in a habitat.

returns._0: The amount of nectar, pollen, and sap in the habitat.

getInitialHabitatResources(uint256).details: Get the initial resources in a habitat.

returns._0: The amount of nectar, pollen, and sap in the habitat.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

Cs().notice: Cn ,Cp ,Cs are constants that adjust the scale of resources gathered to fit the game's economy and balance. These constants can be used to fine-tune how rewarding foraging feels in the game Make sure to adjust these constants carefully to ensure the game is not too easy or too hard
